This paper involves the use of machine learning techniques for forecasting, which falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with the optimization of demand-side management, which can be categorized under "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI) and "Systems and Control" (cs.SY). The use of hierarchical techniques for improving forecasting performance suggests the possibility of the paper being categorized under "Data Structures and Algorithms" (cs.DS) or "Software Engineering" (cs.SE).
